scripts.text: A battered and faded sign stands alongside the road...
Judging from how the road beneath your feet vanishes into the waters of the swamp right in front of you, you suspect that the sign may be a little out of date.

You stoop and enter the low hut. The floor is muddy and dank, and the stench is almost unbearable. In the center of the hut, a cold fire pit is filled with bones and ashes. Most of the bones appear to have been chewed on...

mouseClickScript.mazeScript: Writhing Mire to Ruins Of Hail
